Definition: a crystalline compound that has the cool and minty taste and odor that occurs naturally in peppermint oil
Example: used as a flavoring and in medicine to relieve itching, pain, and nasal congestion
Synonyms: compound, noun, food, peppermint_oil, s, artifact, mentholated_salve, a, crystalline, that, has, the, cool, and, minty, taste, odor, occurs, naturally, in, peppermint, oil, used, as, flavoring, medicine, to, relieve, itching, pain, nasal, congestion
Category: noun.substance
